des:
Think you know your music? Check out our awesome game for Kids, Song Jam!

From the creators of Beat The Intro by Musicplode Media, Song Jam is the awesome new music guessing game for Kids. Choose your playlist from movies and party to TikTok and Disney and play a match against another player from around the world.

To get started, just say: “Alexa, open Song Jam!”
